          <l n="b"><milestone n="b" unit="column"></milestone>śrutvā stutyā namas-kr̥tā</l>
          <l n="c"><lb n="A8"></lb><milestone n="a" unit="column"></milestone>Anu<space type="descender"></space>ka<space type="descender"></space>thyā mayā bhaktyā</l>
